OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few heavy
OL,6,Fshowers will tend to die out this
OL,7,Fevening. The rest of the night will
OL,8,Fsee further showers across western
OL,9,Fareas, but drier around the east coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,12,Fscattered showers. Turning brighter
OL,13,Fthrough the afternoon with some
OL,14,Fsunnier spells developing and showers
OL,15,Fbecoming fewer later. Breezy.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FPatchy
OL,18,Fcloud developing on Sunday alongside
OL,19,Frisk of showers later. A few showers
OL,20,Fon Monday but mostly dry by Tuesday.
OL,21,FWinds lighter than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
